{"tid":1724881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣樂團滅火器搵林夕寫咗首《雙城記》俾香港","createTime":"2019-11-15T14:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T16:58:12.000Z","uid":104721,"like":179,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"95976fb78b0304b1303efeb5a851201a0a9c50a8","tid":1724881,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ERZboYStq0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FERZboYStq0w&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=374ea8d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ERZboYStq0w</a><br />\n<br />\n夕爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我愛大正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《雙城記 City of Sadness》<br />\n編曲：鄭宇辰 ORio Cheng、Mike Green、滅火器 Fire EX.<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：楊大正 Sam Yang<br />\nOP：Denseline Co Limited (Warner Chappell Music, Hong Kong Limited)/ 火氣音樂股份有限公司 FIRE ON MUSIC Co., LTD.<br />\nSP：Warner Chappell Music, Hong Kong Limited Taiwan Branch/ 相知國際股份有限公司 BETWEEN Co., LTD.<br />\n尾奏改編原曲：神思者（S.E.N.S）悲情城市（主題曲）<br />\n <br />\n無辜的人 / 昨天已犯了明天的罪<br />\n​有心的人 / 原罪是沒本事諂媚<br />\n​無臉的人 / 受不起被餵飽的恩惠<br />\n​有夢的人 / 再也沒有自由閉嘴<br />\n <br />\n​漂白了城市的淚 / 煙霧不必再催<br />\n​螻蟻只有汗水 / 歷史總在輪迴<br />\n哪裡沒紀念碑 / 哪種悲情更悲<br />\n <br />\n​他們用彈藥回答 / 不中聽的喧嘩<br />\n​寒蟬只能 / 在沈默中爆發<br />\n冷血是冷血者的大麻<br />\n​熱血讓熱血者 / 走到遍地開花<br />\n <br />\n​他們用黑手打壓 / 赤裸裸施行家法<br />\n​我們用流水 / 變成盔甲<br />\n無恥逼迫出無畏的人<br />\n在權威之下 / 無權說害怕（我們無權害怕）<br />\n <br />\n少年人渺小 / 因而偉大<br />\n​就看誰更快崩塌<br />\n​白色恐怖最怕光明正大<br />\n​老大何時才長大<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊星期日台灣仲有場【 撐香港，要自由 演唱會】<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TW.HK.FreedomIsNotFree/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTW.HK.FreedomIsNotFree%2F&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=f6ee8117\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TW.HK.FreedomIsNotFree/</a>"},{"pid":"88ab539219cbcd4aba0c94bf3de4bb966355cb4e","tid":1724881,"uid":190793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36d836d75e52020a6ef8a45d2bef94628024a474","tid":1724881,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcc1855ceb021081d462787353648cee2d1f6400","tid":1724881,"uid":104721,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"本身佢地想講台灣228事件，點知係金曲獎撞到林夕，就邀請咗夕爺幫佢地寫歌，於是結合而成咗呢首雙城記"},{"pid":"532009810813e79c5aabf489b90bc6f0454f80c6","tid":1724881,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835be1ec8849acf6c8916a0d9a3065afa6722667","tid":1724881,"uid":168267,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"其實雙城記本書本身都好正<br />\n例如入面啲起義嘅法國人，未革命時會用靜靜雞mark低啲打壓過佢哋嘅仆街落張清算名單度<br />\n革命軍唔會叫大家個名，互相稱呼做Jacques，類似我哋嘅「手足」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35abf8c3112311508206716170418a3e1637ffb","tid":1724881,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"lp"},{"pid":"704742688004ed8a613ccfccc1b761e471522e21","tid":1724881,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-